      },
      "date": "2015-01-23 20:29:49.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nWouldn't it make sense to migrate released files like this:\n  - Open volatile file with O_LOV_DELAY_CREAT\n  - Assign it the desired stripe\n  - Swap layouts with the released file\n\nThis is totally untested, but I believe it could work and prevent from having to restore released files for the sole purpose of migrating them.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 1
    },
    {
