        },
        "subject": "LU-5895 lfs: prevent migration of a released file",
        "message": "LU-5895 lfs: prevent migration of a released file\n\nIf a file has been released, and a migrate operation is performed on it,\nthe file will be implicitely restored, then swapped, but this leads to\nthe following error:\n\n lfs: <file name>: data version changed during migration\n error: migrate: migrate stripe file '<file name>' failed\n\nBefore trying to migrate a file, check whether it is released and\nprevent the migration in this case.\n\nSigned-off-by: frank zago <fzago@cray.com>\nSigned-off-by: Henri Doreau <henri.doreau@cea.fr>\nChange-Id: I53fda64ab24f6119919f7c84bd4db9aff0d7e025\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
